{"tid":1099201,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[24小時無休TG谷] 狼人殺! 阿瓦隆! 誰是牛頭王!","createTime":"2019-04-09T15:30:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T02:20:24.000Z","uid":70910,"like":7,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fa8b13061eb8ab506f9c7b0945fb9a13df658fcc","tid":1099201,"uid":70910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T15:30:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>係咪覺得好悶想搵野玩呢?</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">番shift冇野做想吹下水?</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">即刻加入我地啦! <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">狼人殺! </span> <span style=\"color: maroon;\">阿瓦隆! </span> <span style=\"color: red;\">誰是牛頭王! </span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">24小時無間斷開game 99%齊5人或以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">只要你覺悶想搵人一齊玩  Click個start制 就自然有人陪你踢走寂寞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">谷內規則好簡單!<br />\n玩果陣唔準cap圖cap對話。<br />\n唔準鳩衝女狼友，要互助互愛，發揮村民精神！緊記無遺無deadtalk.<br />\n唔好Troll Game阿!!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>即刻填表入谷啦!</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/tCuaPQrCdC5aKhzi1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FtCuaPQrCdC5aKhzi1&d=se%2BVxgw3JrdCjNobn1OhIgbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=5a4ae912\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/tCuaPQrCdC5aKhzi1</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>放心 填form只係為左避免有人亂入搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地並唔會filter走任何巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></div></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">如果你玩game率太低 有機會被踢走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以入得谷 就要多啲玩!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></span></strong></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f305021e534337510302c80e8d057eefa71fbc94","tid":1099201,"uid":70910,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T23:06:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"852e4dc80f90efc7ccbe8d5999acc5d9d5ceecb0","tid":1099201,"uid":70910,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T01:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i